<P>Here is a list of all the trinkets I know of and the maximum level you can be 
before they start being worth negative points. Some are very awkward to get, so 
don't worry if you can't find them; I doubt whether many of even our most 
experienced players have seen the <FONT color=#00eeee>frogspawn</FONT>, for 
example! 
