<P><h2>Exercises</h2> 
<P>Don't worry if you can't do these exercises all in one reset. Other people 
may have moved the objects concerned - particularly if they, too, were doing 
these exercises! Spread them out over several resets if necessary. Although they 
don't have to be attempted in order, the ones at the beginning of the list are 
probably easier than the ones toward the end. 
<OL>
 <LI>Go to the lounge in the cottage and pick up any treasure there, then drop 
 it in the swamp. 
 <LI>Go to the fitted wardrobe in the cottage and pick up any treasure there. 
 Mind you're not carrying too much - it's a small room. 
 <LI>Read the map in the cottage. 
 <LI>Hit the toy drum at the bandstand. 
 <LI>Find the shrine - it's not far from the bandstand. 
 <LI>Find the tomahawk in the villa. 
 <LI>Eat the grapes at the pergola - it's <b>w.s</b> from the fountain in the 
 formal garden. 
 <LI>Find the place where the bonsai trees grow. 
 <LI>Find the posy vase and put a flower in it. 
 <LI>Ring the altar bell. </LI></OL>
